The Property Investment Seminar is making a resounding return to the city of Johannesburg. Being hosted by Private Property in partnership with Prosperity Enterprises at Radisson Blu Hotel in Sandton on the 2nd of July 2022, this one-day event is part of an innovative and strategic plan by these key industry stakeholders to unlock and unveil excellent property investment opportunities. The event will also create and cement industry linkages and platforms for enhancing knowledge and putting the power of property investment in the hands of the people. Structured in an interactive, inspiring, and fun way, this seminar will provide aspiring and established property investors with tangible tools, tried and tested profitable investment strategies and reputable expert guidance which is essential in climbing the property investment and ownership ladder. Topical subject matters to be addressed by Jaco Grobbelaar and Ewan Rourke who are sought after business leaders and property speakers will include: Jaco enjoys a glowing reputation for being the pioneer of Prosperity Enterprises and is an international speaker, investment structuring expert and property investor. Ewan Rourke, is a serial entrepreneur, speaker and shrewd business strategist. Tickets for the Investment Seminar, which are available as single or double tickets, are competitively priced and offer attendees unbelievable returns on investment. Early bird special prices offer ends on the 23rd of June. Tickets can be booked by calling 021 441 3000 or emailing seminars@prosperityenterprises.co.za. One on one consultation Discount voucher is available, at a 20% discount.